{
  "text": "Similar to Fomin et al. [CITATION_1] , we define a class of graph problems in NP which we call graph subset problems where the goal is to find a subset of vertices satisfying some property. We show a meta theorem showing that a restricted class of graph subset problems that are in NP admit log-space exponential algorithms in the rotate and implicit models.",
